解決到，唔得先問人 同埋記得用「想向你請教下」相關詞語去問人幫手<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">以上只係小小個人意見，唔岩聽請skip，謝謝</span>"},{"pid":"fc7c12bec300834f92c5bcc2b8bea30ff5982e19","tid":1160313,"uid":12696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"698ada3b9b3b9d2cabca47ee5e56d6d94d7d7d35","tid":1160313,"uid":65220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f5e1a6a4aa6f78104bf5f09f6c3895400175fe8","tid":1160313,"uid":12696,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:41:27.000Z","msg":"上年grad鳩完大半年<br />\n月頭開始番<br />\n日日都想QUIT<br />\n但係又唔知做乜<br />\n得個工程degree<br />\n人工算高但係好撚辛苦<br />\n寧願低人工做份舒服D既工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T17:39:12.000Z","msg":"咁巴打你打唔打算繼續做呀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T02:48:53.000Z","msg":"重做緊<br />\n唔知點同條女同老母交待<br />\n好撚濕滯"},{"pid":"af42fb7969b0a1b38c24d2364f550ba848dbcfa9","tid":1160313,"uid":181439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"981d03bcf0702667fb0b9eefac53f1366c3ec6fe","tid":1160313,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"491b6d3e2561ec3ebb607736a894725065e20b51","tid":1160313,"uid":187108,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:36:41.000Z","msg":"點解會俾人炒先？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:37:54.000Z","msg":"做得慢、學得慢，唔醒目"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:08:21.000Z","msg":"唔醒目 都唔係太緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係學得慢 就大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岩岩畢業應該仲係吸收力最強時段<br />\n除非過多幾年 人老左 先至記憶力下降<br />\n後生年紀一定係學野快<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}